 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I want to be included in all the weird nerd things!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/euCrQSI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>No idea what this is about</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hAzBTpk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh lord. It’s shrek all over again</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JNfbJs5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I got conned into buying lemonade from some neighbor kids and they were charging like $4 a cup and they had a card reader??? I had no excuse and then it was FUCKING MINUTE MAID I nearly threw it into a kids face</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kj7cavn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Omg that spider is so cute</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CcTPHY4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don’t know why but this pic makes me laugh every time</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6fBzAEy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I can HEAR it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZbTCNop.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Meeeeee</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lESZecK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Green is me. Also, in what universe is that fox green?!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AlSohkA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Literally all that bitch had to do was shut her mouth forever and fuck off into the sunset. Why.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6NGfU6q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But what about the guys who like big dicks in their mouths</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J4vcenz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I sent this to someone I know who’s a KFC executive but he says they won’t sell them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e1QS5R7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Besties, would you rather a) let a dude know he has disappointed you and make him do the job right or b) fake an orgasm and just get outta there? No wrong answers.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2T7wBsm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More memes I sent to my KFC guy that he ignored</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PirohOC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There’s no wrong path my friend, everyone has their purpose, mine is just stabbin peeps</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XNG9nVg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There’s like a 90% chance I’d either die or want to die</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w9idLZZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Life IS weird but so am I!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xV0ZwAK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don’t have my glasses on so for all I know it could be a kiwi. Or cake.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PqWf2ow.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s me I’m a feral hoe</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xiIP9Bh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Meh</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QnItu0H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Give a bunch of monkeys enough time with a typewriter and eventually they’ll reinvent Shakespeare…. Nah tumblr is just the Wild West of weird and it fucking acts like it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tCDuHy7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sigh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ThISPQX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Is there a way to do this with an entire relationship? Just abort mission when it gets too awkward?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0x4hzex.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yep. A nice lovely blend of proteins, fats, and carbs.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nN7ze0z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is the most Texas thing I’ve ever seen, except Whataburger didn’t make it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KC0i2s9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The chaos gremlin in me would uninvite Grandma just to see what happens</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3US6Vgn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I actually just busted out my favorite toys to give to my baby. They’re Barbie’s and he’s a boy but no one cares except my mom and she’s had it too easy for too li</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SoIxkfI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know fang bangers are convenient but god at what cost</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IBh6wUC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Life gets a lot simpler when you’re whatever kind of autistic I am where everyone ends up fucking hating you. It’s just a matter of time before they get upset with you so you just do your thing without regards to their stupid neurotypical feelings that make no sense</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YRwQgob.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dragon!!!!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z5X17gG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And both are ridiculously easy!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4K4L65M.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Make sure to balance human flesh with vegetables and fish to avoid getting the shakes</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/msW50hQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think this is an ad but it amused me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dinkbpJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s weird being this good at something I utterly loathe. Like my brains default is “jump off a bridge and die” and yet I have that dumbass part of it trussed up and full of bear tranqs in the back while the rest of me is having a blast</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lhlgxCX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I really like this quote. Also “I love you on purpose” - Casey McQuiston. RED WHITE AND ROYAL BLUE is so damn good</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D4ZMn2c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What in the goddamn fuck is our world</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2Vh9NDC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I would pay so much money for one of these. The stupid one I got was digital and fuckin erased itself after a few days.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MmAqi0A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sounds gay im in</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xjVCfT4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>No. No they are not. Probably idk</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CzQCHfd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I need an escape hatch for when I’ve overestimated my social abilities</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2JEnmpU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Doggie tax! 

I usually tell a story so ummmmmm last night the baby was very fussy and so I passed him off to my husband bc I’ve been sick and he’s had it too easy lately and I heard them watching animal videos on YouTube and my husband is just chattering away and then he gets desperate I guess and goes “do you know the tale of darth plagius the wise?” And then PROCEEDS TO FUCKING BUTCHER THE SPEECH I am seriously considering divorce I don’t even like the prequels and I still know it by heart he is embarrassing the family and setting a bad example for my son</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4jJKVoG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kirbyvictorious]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Finish him!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gFh7RrE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/g8Zb3ka.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Definitely a repost, no idea what the source is, but funny regardless</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gFh7RrE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[FromTheBeyond]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is how to stop your wife shopping.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HQjyT7W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JmD6lvE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HQjyT7W</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JaSphere1111]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I scoff at them</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AGCuqpp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ojgl0iA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AGCuqpp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CeleryMan7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Somebody’s feeling a little extra today</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7aQYl1C</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DVp2xhb.gif" st